Description: A suite of tools for single cell copy number analysis 
        focusing on reads binning, segmentation, normalization, 
        filtering, analysis, and visualization. CopyKit can perform
        pre-processing, QC, copy number inference,
        and subclone clustering to delineate the clonal diversity of tumors.
